title: Normal Chapter #01
description:
The story of a 16 year old girl, the only person in the world who doesn't have superpowers.

She and her companions must try and survive in a world where governments, rogue military units, supremacist groups and religious zealots are hunting her, desperate to achieve their own agendas.

The creator Colin Wells has made the first chapter available for Torrents users to legally download, read and share as you choose.

You're welcome :)

The webcomic is available to read free at http://normalcomic.cfw.me
